Upgraded to v3.0.1 of JS8Call.
The QRPLabs QMX option .... appears to work!  
No SIGSEGV.

I observe this version has a pop warning me I have been idle for 60 minutes.
What's that all about?

JS8Call / General / Networking & Autoreply 
"idle timeout: disable autoreply after".
So the timeout is to prevent your machine from generating msgs when you are away.
